sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_matsa_sdlc_lite.SDLCliteUtilsd</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>SDLCliteUtilsd</name><script><![CDATA[var SDLCliteUtilsd = Class.create();
SDLCliteUtilsd.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},
	
	
	type: 'SDLCliteUtilsd'
};

SDLCliteUtilsd.getSprintTeamPoints = function (sprint) {
	var nTeamPoints = 0;
	if (sprint) {
		var sprintTeamMember = new GlideRecord ("x_matsa_sdlc_lite_sprint_team_member");
		sprintTeamMember.addQuery("sprint", sprint.sys_id);
		sprintTeamMember.query();
		while (sprintTeamMember.next()) {
			nTeamPoints += sprintTeamMember.planned_points;
		}
	}
	return nTeamPoints;
};

SDLCliteUtilsd.getSprintStoryPoints = function (sprint) {
	var nStoryPoints = 0;
	if (sprint) {
		var recRmStory = new GlideAggregate("x_matsa_sdlc_lite_story");
		recRmStory.addQuery("sprint", sprint.sys_id);
		recRmStory.addQuery("state", "!=", 107);   // 107 means "Cancelled"
		recRmStory.addAggregate("SUM", "points");
		recRmStory.groupBy("sprint");
		recRmStory.query();
		if (recRmStory.next()) {
			nStoryPoints = recRmStory.getAggregate("SUM", "points");
		}
	}
	return nStoryPoints;
};

SDLCliteUtilsd.getSprintStoryPoints_completed = function (sprint) {
	var nStoryPoints = 0;
	if (sprint) {
		var recRmStory = new GlideAggregate("x_matsa_sdlc_lite_story");
		recRmStory.addQuery("sprint", sprint.sys_id);
		recRmStory.addQuery("state", 106);   // 106 means "Completed"
		recRmStory.addAggregate("SUM", "points");
		recRmStory.groupBy("sprint");
		recRmStory.query();
		if (recRmStory.next()) {
			nStoryPoints = recRmStory.getAggregate("SUM", "points");
		}
	}
	return nStoryPoints;
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-10-02 20:25:33</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>0e37f73ddb2583405dbe38f0ad9619ed</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SDLCliteUtilsd</sys_name><sys_package display_value="SDLC lite" source="x_matsa_sdlc_lite">aab78b71dbe183405dbe38f0ad96199d</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="SDLC lite">aab78b71dbe183405dbe38f0ad96199d</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_0e37f73ddb2583405dbe38f0ad9619ed</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>brent.llewellyn</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-10-03 12:38:41</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_matsa_sdlc_lite_sprint_team_member</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Check for duplicate</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	// Add your code here
	if( isDuplicate(current) ) {
		gs.addErrorMessage(gs.getMessage('User is already added to the team'));
		current.setAbortAction(true);
	}

function isDuplicate(_current) {
	var gr = new GlideRecord('x_matsa_sdlc_lite_sprint_team_member');
	gr.addQuery('name', _current.name);
	gr.addQuery('sprint',_current.sprint);
	gr.addQuery('sys_id','!=',_current.sys_id);
	gr.query();
    var count = gr.getRowCount();
	gs.info('count: '+count)
